  "prompt": "How do I solve the following question in HackerRank?",
  "response": "To provide an accurate and helpful response to your question about solving a specific HackerRank problem, I'll need more details about the question itself. HackerRank has a wide variety of coding challenges, and the approach to solving them can vary significantly depending on the problem.\n\nTo help you effectively, please provide the following information:\n\n1. The exact title or description of the HackerRank problem you're working on.\n2. The programming language you want to use to solve it.\n3. Any specific parts of the problem that you're struggling with.\n4. Any code you've already written or attempted.\n\nOnce you provide this information, I can offer a step-by-step solution, explain the key concepts involved, and help you understand the problem better. This will allow me to give you a more tailored and useful response to help you succeed in solving the HackerRank challenge.",
